<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">Pennywise's Offer</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
It is an ancient, demonic being who dwells in the sewers under Derry. Its Spider form; Clown form; and the Deadlights can all be seen as an evil version of the Holy Trinity. Much like other demonic entities, It tries to make a deal with the Losers Club promising that it would leave them alone if they were to allow it to take Bill instead.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="hep8ka">
<input type="hidden" name="is_logged_in" value="0">
